<div class="title">A Wonderful Bad Experience</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamines (Adderall)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Slinging+Pills&Exact=1">Slinging Pills</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Slinging Pills. "A Wonderful Bad Experience: An Experience with Amphetamines (Adderall) (exp9686)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jul 8, 2005. erowid.org/exp/9686</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
